we-want-to-go-home-us-travel-blogger-breaks-down-as-hantavirus-outbreak-kills-3-on-atlantic-cruise-ship/articleshow/130825509.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T15:53:35+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130825634,imgsize-101736.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[NASA just turned a retired Boeing 777 into a powerful airborne science lab: How a passenger jet became a flying laboratory for 100 scientists]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130819438.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/nasa-just-turned-a-retired-boeing-777-into-a-powerful-airborne-science-lab-how-a-passenger-jet-became-a-flying-laboratory-for-100-scientists/articleshow/130819438.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/nasa-just-turned-a-retired-boeing-777-into-a-powerful-airborne-science-lab-how-a-passenger-jet-became-a-flying-laboratory-for-100-scientists/articleshow/130819438.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T12:39:23+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130819462,imgsize-92230.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ukraine, Russia announce separate ceasefires ahead of Moscow’s Victory Day]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130815208.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Ukraine announced a ceasefire starting May 5-6, prioritizing human life over Victory Day commemorations, with President Zelenskyy criticizing Russia's focus on parades. Russia, however, declared its own truce from May 8-9, coinciding with WWII Victory Day, and warned of massive retaliation if Kyiv disrupts their celebrations.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-russia-announce-separate-ceasefires-ahead-of-moscows-victory-day/articleshow/130815208.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-russia-announce-separate-ceasefires-ahead-of-moscows-victory-day/articleshow/130815208.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T09:27:20+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130815555,imgsize-325148.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Why were Louis Sammartino reaction videos struck? YouTuber Outdoor Boys move fuels LosPollosTV copyright fight and online outrage]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130813230.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Louis Sammartino’s LosPollosTV faces backlash after Outdoor Boys content linked to Luke Nichols triggers copyright strikes. His viral reaction clip and his father’s “disturbing” remark fueled debate. Fans largely backed original creators, questioning reaction videos. The clash highlights a bigger issue, how fair use works online and where creators draw the line between content sharing and ownership.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-were-louis-sammartino-reaction-videos-struck-youtuber-outdoor-boys-move-fuels-lospollostv-copyright-fight-and-online-outrage/articleshow/130813230.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/why-were-louis-sammartino-reaction-videos-struck-youtuber-outdoor-boys-move-fuels-lospollostv-copyright-fight-and-online-outrage/articleshow/130813230.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T04:45:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sehjal Gupta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130813223,imgsize-1286055.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Gun scare near White House: Person shot by law enforcement at Washington Monument]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130811337.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Law enforcement shot an individual near the Washington Monument on Monday, triggering a brief White House lockdown. Emergency services transported an adult male to the hospital, while a teenager received treatment for minor injuries. The incident, occurring close to a presidential event, adds to recent security concerns in the capital.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/gun-scare-near-white-house-person-shot-by-law-enforcement-at-washington-monument-lockdown-briefly-imposed/articleshow/130811337.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/gun-scare-near-white-house-person-shot-by-law-enforcement-at-washington-monument-lockdown-briefly-imposed/articleshow/130811337.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T02:51:58+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130811365,imgsize-1360280.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Chirayu Rana took leave for dad's death in 2024 but his father is alive; says he doesn't know anything about JP Morgan row]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130811322.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/chirayu-rana-took-leave-for-dads-death-in-2024-but-his-father-is-alive-says-he-doesnt-know-anything-about-jp-morgan-row/articleshow/130811322.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/chirayu-rana-took-leave-for-dads-death-in-2024-but-his-father-is-alive-says-he-doesnt-know-anything-about-jp-morgan-row/articleshow/130811322.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T02:39:49+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130811328,imgsize-24478.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘My goal was not immigration’: Oxford law graduate chooses India to avoid future regret]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130821754.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/my-goal-was-not-immigration-oxford-law-graduate-on-why-shes-returning-to-india-from-uk/articleshow/130821754.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/my-goal-was-not-immigration-oxford-law-graduate-on-why-shes-returning-to-india-from-uk/articleshow/130821754.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-05T13:42:41+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-130822770,imgsize-127532.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Viral clip shows IShowSpeed landing punch on fan during Puerto Rico appearance]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/130811279.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Popular streamer IShowSpeed's recent public appearance in Puerto Rico took a dramatic turn when a playful boxing-style moment with a fan went viral.  During a meet-up, Speed landed a strong punch, causing the fan to stumble, which quickly ignited online discussions and exaggerated claims of a knockout. This incident highlights the unpredictable nature of his content tours.]]></description><link><![C